These are the source files for Arch Linux packages made at Kozea.

Packages are:

gedit-source-code-browser-git
    The *Source Code Browser* plugin for Gedit 3

gedit-whitespace-terminator-git
    The *Whitespace terminator* plugin for Gedit 3

thunderbird-ldap
    A dirty hack to work around Thunderbird bug #292127 ie. Thunderbird
    segfaults when started by a Unix used identified with pam_ldap.

    This package brutally overwrites Thunderbirdâ€™s libldap with the system one.
    See https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=292127#c6

kozea-stuff
    Dependency package to easily install stuff we usually need.
